@@ -30,7 +30,9 @@
 'libffa' will build recursively.
 
 to run:
-./bin/ffa_calc WIDTH HEIGHT
+./bin/peh WIDTH HEIGHT TAPESPACE LIFE [RNG]
 
 WIDTH  must be a... see libffa/fz_lim.ads.
 HEIGHT must be equal to or great than 1.
+TAPESPACE must be at or below the maximum set in limits.ads.
+LIFE may be any bus-width integer (0 gives "immortal" run.)
